<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Kage-Script Pipeline Benchmark</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Spectral:wght@200;300;400&family=Inter:wght@400;500;700&family=IBM+Plex+Mono:wght@500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  :root {
    --bg:        #F8FAFC;
    --surface:   #F1F5F9;
    --border:    #E2E8F0;
    --text:      #1A1B1F;
    --text-sec:  #334155;
    --text-ter:  #64748B;
    --teal:      #10676F;
    --mint:      #1DCD98;
    --cyan:      #35A4B9;
    --sand:      #E3A880;
    --coral:     #DB8577;
    --red:       #FF6467;
    --shadow-card: 0 50px 14px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.00),0 32px 13px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.01),0 18px 11px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.04),0 8px 8px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.06),0 2px 4px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.07);
  }

  html { background: var(--bg); color: var(--text); font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.75; }

  body { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 40px 24px 80px; }

  /* ── Header ── */
  .header { margin-bottom: 40px; }
  .header h1 {
    font-family: 'Spectral', serif; font-weight: 200; font-size: 48px;
    line-height: 110%; letter-spacing: -1.44px; color: var(--text-sec);
  }
  .header .subtitle {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--text-ter);
    margin-top: 8px;
  }
  .header-meta {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; margin-top: 12px; flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .header-meta a {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--teal);
    text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(16,103,111,0.3);
  }
  .header-meta a:hover { border-bottom-color: var(--teal); }
  .save-status {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--text-ter);
    margin-left: auto;
  }
  .save-status.saving { color: var(--sand); }
  .save-status.saved  { color: var(--mint); }
  .save-status.failed { color: var(--red); }

  /* ── Summary Cards ── */
  .cards { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 16px; margin-bottom: 40px; }
  @media (max-width: 800px) { .cards { grid-template-columns: repeat(2,1fr); } }
  .card {
    background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 24px 20px; box-shadow: var(--shadow-card);
  }
  .card-label {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--text-ter); margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .card-value {
    font-family: 'Spectral', serif; font-size: 32px; font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 130%; letter-spacing: -0.96px; color: var(--text-sec);
  }
  .card-delta {
    display: inline-block; margin-top: 8px; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--mint); background: rgba(29,205,152,0.1); border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 2px 8px;
  }
  .card-sub { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-ter); margin-top: 4px; }

  /* ── Chart ── */
  .section-title {
    font-family: 'Spectral', serif; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: -0.6px; color: var(--text-sec); margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .chart-wrap { background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 20px; padding: 28px 24px; box-shadow: var(--shadow-card); margin-bottom: 40px; }
  .chart-legend { display: flex; gap: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .legend-item { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-sec); }
  .legend-dot { width: 10px; height: 10px; border-radius: 3px; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .legend-old { background: var(--sand); }
  .legend-new { background: var(--teal); }

  .chart-rows { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; }
  .chart-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 100px 1fr 1fr 44px; align-items: center; gap: 8px; }
  .chart-band-label { font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.5px; color: var(--text-ter); text-align: right; }
  .bar-group { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 3px; }
  .bar-track { height: 10px; background: var(--border); border-radius: 4px; overflow: hidden; }
  .bar-fill { height: 100%; border-radius: 4px; transition: width 0.4s ease; min-width: 2px; }
  .bar-fill-old { background: var(--sand); }
  .bar-fill-new { background: var(--teal); }
  .chart-count { font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-ter); font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; }

  /* ── Callout ── */
  .callout { background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 20px; padding: 24px 24px; box-shadow: var(--shadow-card); margin-bottom: 40px; }
  .callout-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(260px,1fr)); gap: 16px; margin-top: 16px; }
  .callout-item { border-radius: 12px; padding: 14px 16px; border: 1px solid transparent; }
  .callout-win   { background: rgba(29,205,152,0.07); border-color: rgba(29,205,152,0.25); }
  .callout-warn  { background: rgba(255,100,103,0.06); border-color: rgba(255,100,103,0.2); }
  .callout-note  { background: rgba(53,164,185,0.07); border-color: rgba(53,164,185,0.2); }
  .callout-item-title { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text-sec); margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .callout-item-body  { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-ter); line-height: 1.5; }
  .pill {
    display: inline-block; border-radius: 6px; padding: 1px 7px;
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px; margin: 0 2px;
  }
  .pill-teal  { background: rgba(16,103,111,0.1); color: var(--teal); }
  .pill-mint  { background: rgba(29,205,152,0.12); color: #0d9f74; }
  .pill-coral { background: rgba(219,133,119,0.12); color: #b85a48; }
  .pill-red   { background: rgba(255,100,103,0.1); color: #c93a3c; }

  /* ── Controls ── */
  .controls { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 10px; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .filter-group { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 6px; }
  .filter-btn {
    height: 32px; padding: 0 12px; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid var(--border);
    background: var(--surface); color: var(--text-sec); font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 12px; font-weight: 500; cursor: pointer; transition: background 0.15s, border-color 0.15s;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .filter-btn:hover { background: var(--border); }
  .filter-btn.active {
    background: linear-gradient(208deg, #3C3F43 13.06%, #23242A 82.45%);
    border-color: transparent; color: #F8FAFC; font-weight: 700;
  }
  .search-input {
    height: 32px; padding: 0 12px; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid var(--border);
    background: var(--surface); color: var(--text); font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 13px; width: 220px; outline: none;
  }
  .search-input:focus { border-color: var(--teal); }
  .sort-select {
    height: 32px; padding: 0 10px; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid var(--border);
    background: var(--surface); color: var(--text-sec); font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 12px; font-weight: 500; cursor: pointer; outline: none;
  }
  .sort-select:focus { border-color: var(--teal); }

  /* ── Table ── */
  .table-wrap { overflow-x: auto; border-radius: 20px; border: 1px solid var(--border); box-shadow: var(--shadow-card); }
  table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; background: white; font-size: 13px; }
  thead { background: var(--surface); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 2; }
  thead th {
    padding: 10px 12px; text-align: left; font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-ter); white-space: nowrap;
  }
  thead th:first-child { width: 40px; text-align: center; }
  tbody tr { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); transition: background 0.1s; cursor: default; }
  tbody tr:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  tbody tr:hover { background: #F8FAFC; }
  td { padding: 10px 12px; vertical-align: top; }
  td:first-child { text-align: center; color: var(--text-ter); font-size: 11px; font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace; }
  .cell-text {
    display: block; max-width: 220px; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis;
    white-space: nowrap; color: var(--text); cursor: help;
  }
  .cell-text.orig { font-weight: 500; }
  .cell-text.dimmed { color: var(--text-ter); }
  .sim-badge {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    min-width: 52px; height: 22px; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    letter-spacing: 0.3px; white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .sim-green { background: rgba(29,205,152,0.12); color: #0d9f74; }
  .sim-yellow { background: rgba(227,168,128,0.15); color: #a06030; }
  .sim-red   { background: rgba(255,100,103,0.1); color: #c93a3c; }
  .delta-badge {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    min-width: 58px; height: 22px; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700; font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    letter-spacing: 0.3px; white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .delta-pos { background: rgba(29,205,152,0.10); color: #0d9f74; }
  .delta-neg { background: rgba(255,100,103,0.08); color: #c93a3c; }
  .delta-zero { background: var(--border); color: var(--text-ter); }
  .exact-star { color: var(--teal); font-size: 11px; margin-left: 3px; }

  .table-footer { padding: 10px 16px; font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-ter); background: var(--surface); border-top: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 0 0 20px 20px; }
  .hidden-row { display: none; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- Header -->
<header class="header">
  <h1>Kage-Script Pipeline Benchmark</h1>
  <p class="subtitle">101 sentences &middot; encode &rarr; decode round-trip accuracy</p>
  <div class="header-meta">
    <a href="https://github.com/Wake4188/kage-script" target="_blank" rel="noopener">github.com/Wake4188/kage-script</a>
    <span class="save-status" id="saveStatus"></span>
  </div>
</header>

<!-- Summary Cards -->
<div class="cards" id="summaryCards">
  <div class="card">
    <div class="card-label">Avg Similarity</div>
    <div class="card-value">71.25%</div>
    <div class="card-sub">Old pipeline</div>
  </div>
  <div class="card">
    <div class="card-label">Avg Similarity</div>
    <div class="card-value" style="color: var(--teal);">84.76%</div>
    <span class="card-delta">+13.51 pp</span>
    <div class="card-sub">New pipeline</div>
  </div>
  <div class="card">
    <div class="card-label">Exact Matches</div>
    <div class="card-value">11 <span style="font-size:18px; color:var(--text-ter);">/ 101</span></div>
    <div class="card-sub">Old pipeline &nbsp;&mdash;&nbsp; 10.9%</div>
  </div>
  <div class="card">
    <div class="card-label">Exact Matches</div>
    <div class="card-value" style="color: var(--teal);">26 <span style="font-size:18px; color:var(--text-ter);">/ 101</span></div>
    <span class="card-delta">+15 more</span>
    <div class="card-sub">New pipeline &nbsp;&mdash;&nbsp; 25.7%</div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- Distribution Chart -->
<section class="chart-wrap">
  <h2 class="section-title">Similarity Score Distribution</h2>
  <div class="chart-legend">
    <div class="legend-item"><div class="legend-dot legend-old"></div> Old pipeline</div>
    <div class="legend-item"><div class="legend-dot legend-new"></div> New pipeline</div>
  </div>
  <div class="chart-rows" id="chartRows"></div>
</section>

<!-- Notable Patterns -->
<section class="callout">
  <h2 class="section-title">Notable Patterns</h2>
  <div class="callout-grid">
    <div class="callout-item callout-win">
      <div class="callout-item-title">Technical identifiers preserved</div>
      <div class="callout-item-body">
        <span class="pill pill-teal">README</span><span class="pill pill-teal">parseMarkdownToHTML</span><span class="pill pill-teal">TanStack</span>
        &mdash; new pipeline returns exact matches; old pipeline garbles these as phonetic noise.
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="callout-item callout-win">
      <div class="callout-item-title">Proper names preserved</div>
      <div class="callout-item-body">
        <span class="pill pill-teal">Alex</span><span class="pill pill-teal">Maria</span><span class="pill pill-teal">Nguyen</span>
        &mdash; new pipeline returns exact or near-exact results; old pipeline substitutes unrelated words.
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="callout-item callout-win">
      <div class="callout-item-title">File paths &amp; API terms</div>
      <div class="callout-item-body">
        <span class="pill pill-teal">/var/log/app.log</span><span class="pill pill-teal">404 error</span>
        &mdash; new pipeline <span class="pill pill-mint">93.8%</span> and <span class="pill pill-mint">100%</span> vs old pipeline <span class="pill pill-coral">35.5%</span> and <span class="pill pill-coral">52.5%</span>.
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="callout-item callout-note">
      <div class="callout-item-title">Pipeline artifact: &ldquo;bench spacing&rdquo;</div>
      <div class="callout-item-body">
        Old pipeline converts &ldquo;benchmark&rdquo; &rarr; &ldquo;bench spacing&rdquo; or &ldquo;bench space&rdquo; in multiple sentences. New pipeline retains the correct term.
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="callout-item callout-warn">
      <div class="callout-item-title">Word-order reordering &mdash; worst cases</div>
      <div class="callout-item-body">
        Sentences <span class="pill pill-red">#31</span> and <span class="pill pill-red">#96</span> score ~23&ndash;26% for both pipelines. Japanese SOV order completely reorders the clause structure, which neither pipeline recovers.
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="callout-item callout-note">
      <div class="callout-item-title">Sentence #5 &mdash; new loses to old</div>
      <div class="callout-item-body">
        &ldquo;The weather is nice today.&rdquo; &mdash; new returns <span class="pill pill-coral">42.3%</span>, old returns <span class="pill pill-mint">69.4%</span>. The new pipeline expanded the sentence differently.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Table Controls -->
<div class="controls">
  <div class="filter-group" id="filterBtns">
    <button class="filter-btn active" data-filter="all">All</button>
    <button class="filter-btn" data-filter="new-wins">New wins</button>
    <button class="filter-btn" data-filter="old-wins">Old wins</button>
    <button class="filter-btn" data-filter="tied">Tied</button>
    <button class="filter-btn" data-filter="exact-new">Exact (new)</button>
    <button class="filter-btn" data-filter="failed">Failed (&lt;0.6 new)</button>
  </div>
  <input class="search-input" id="searchInput" type="search" placeholder="Search original text...">
  <select class="sort-select" id="sortSelect">
    <option value="index">Sort: Index</option>
    <option value="new-desc">Sort: New sim &darr;</option>
    <option value="new-asc">Sort: New sim &uarr;</option>
    <option value="delta-desc">Sort: Delta &darr;</option>
  </select>
</div>

<!-- Table -->
<div class="table-wrap">
  <table id="benchTable">
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>#</th>
        <th>Original</th>
        <th>Old output</th>
        <th>New output</th>
        <th>Old sim</th>
        <th>New sim</th>
        <th>Delta</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody id="tableBody"></tbody>
  </table>
  <div class="table-footer" id="tableFooter">Showing 101 of 101</div>
</div>

